The First three steps to get involved

Know who your local, state, or federal legislators, politicians, and House Representatives are. There are resources where you can enter your Zip code or address to find them.

Know how to communicate with them and get them to listen to your concerns or questions.

Identify an issue you care about and pursue it Make a list and be prepared to speak on those subjects, providing data, facts, or evidence to aid your points or discussion.

About

DemoCats is a Solana-based token and a play on words for the political party, the Democrats. Cats can be democratic, just ask them and support your local, state, federal, or country leaders by ensuring your voice is heard! Just don't get too carried away...
